long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A bulk assets importer for GIF.COM.AI 

With this extension you can right click to import a single image or use the magic wand to import many images from any website.

Support:

* PNG
* JPG
* GIF
* SVG
* BLOB

Benefits:

★ FREE infinitely scalable decentralized storage. Import dozens, hundreds & thousands of images and lay them out in a virtual light board.

★ Create animated content including memes, cinemagraph & simulations in the gif.com.ai web-top.


SPECIAL NOTE : GIF.COM.AI is more than a toy, it's also an advanced art creation tool with unique creation abilities. Your encouraged to visit the development portal to learn more!
